Class UnknownProgressWrappingTaskMonitor

    TaskMonitor
    public class UnknownProgressWrappingTaskMonitor
extends TaskMonitorAdapter
    A class that is meant to wrap a TaskMonitor when you do not know the maximum value of the progress.
